      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2017 Ford Focus RS, featuring the high-output 2.3L EcoBoost engine equipped with a low-inertia twin-scroll turbocharger. This platform utilizes the sophisticated GKN Twinster torque-vectoring AWD system, capable of diverting up to 70% of torque to the rear axle for neutralized understeer and superior lateral acceleration. The 6-speed manual transmission retains precise gate synchronization, complemented by Brembo four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated rotors for high-thermal-capacity braking. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid service and inspection of the RS-specific adjustable dampers and subframe bushings. The vehicle exhibits excellent structural rigidity and remains in its factory-tuned configuration, providing a raw, visceral driving experience for the performance-oriented enthusiast.",
