      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for example of a modern classic that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though I have noted a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and navigation system, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has a documented service history, including a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh brake service. This car is a reliable, high-quality daily driver that has been garaged and non-smoker owned. It comes complete with two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
